modName: Justin - Nord Nightblade Vampire Lord Level 36 save
summary: Level 36 Nord Nightblade Vampire Lord with no wife or (major) completed questlines
descriptionHtml: Hi!  This is my first upload to this website even though I have been using it for years.  This is my favourite character, and he's been around for a long time.  After almost recently losing him, I've decided to upload him for others to enjoy.  He's a very skilled nightblade vampire with no wife and no completed questlines.  He was originally made on Xbox 360 then moved to PC.  He's completely mod free and fun!
author: Wivvy
